To instantiate the _alpha_m_mod_as_geometric_sum theorem, we want $\ell \mapsto (b_f + \ell)$, but this requires that we establish that $(b_f+\ell) \in \mathbb{Z}$. This we accomplish by noting that $b_f$ is an integer.
